## 5. Animation and Transition Effects

### 5.1 CSS Animations

**Built-in Animations:**
```jsx
className="animate-spin"        // Rotating loader
className="animate-bounce"      // Bouncing effect
className="animate-pulse"       // Pulsing effect (skeleton loading)
```

### 5.2 Transition Effects

**Smooth Transitions:**
```jsx
className="transition-all"      // All properties transition
className="transition-colors"   // Color transitions only
className="hover:opacity-80 transition-all"
className="group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors"
```

**Duration Control:**
```jsx
className="transition-all duration-200"
```

### 5.3 Hover and Interactive States

**Hover Effects:**
```jsx
className="hover:bg-base-300 transition-colors"
className="group-hover:bg-primary/20"
className="hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200"
```

**Group Hover Pattern:**
```jsx
className="group"               // Parent element
className="group-hover:bg-primary/20" // Child responds to parent hover
```

---

## 6. Color and Theming System

### 6.1 DaisyUI Color System

**Semantic Colors:**
- **bg-primary**: Primary background color
- **text-primary**: Primary text color
- **bg-secondary**: Secondary background color
- **bg-accent**: Accent background color
- **bg-neutral**: Neutral background color
- **bg-base-100**: Base background (lightest)
- **bg-base-200**: Base background (medium)
- **bg-base-300**: Base background (darkest)

**Content Colors:**
```jsx
className="text-base-content/60"    // 60% opacity base content
className="text-primary-content"    // Content color for primary backgrounds
```

### 6.2 Opacity Modifiers

**Color Opacity:**
```jsx
className="bg-primary/10"           // 10% opacity primary
className="bg-base-100/80"          // 80% opacity base
className="text-base-content/70"    // 70% opacity text
```

### 6.3 Dynamic Theming

**Theme Switching:**
```jsx
<div data-theme={theme}>            // Theme attribute for dynamic switching
```

**Theme Preview:**
```jsx
<div data-theme={t}>
  <div className="rounded bg-primary"></div>
  <div className="rounded bg-secondary"></div>
  <div className="rounded bg-accent"></div>
  <div className="rounded bg-neutral"></div>
</div>
```

---

## 7. Typography and Text Styling

### 7.1 Font Sizing

**Text Size Scale:**
```jsx
className="text-xs"             // 0.75rem (12px)
className="text-sm"             // 0.875rem (14px)
className="text-base"           // 1rem (16px)
className="text-lg"             // 1.125rem (18px)
className="text-xl"             // 1.25rem (20px)
className="text-2xl"            // 1.5rem (24px)
```

**Custom Font Sizes:**
```jsx
className="text-[11px]"         // Arbitrary value (11px)
className="text-[10px]"         // Arbitrary value (10px)
```

### 7.2 Font Weight and Style

**Font Weights:**
```jsx
className="font-medium"         // 500
className="font-semibold"       // 600
className="font-bold"           // 700
```

### 7.3 Text Alignment and Overflow

**Text Alignment:**
```jsx
className="text-center"         // Center alignment
className="text-left"           // Left alignment
```

**Text Overflow:**
```jsx
className="truncate"            // Ellipsis overflow
className="truncate w-full"     // Full width truncation
```

