## 8. Advanced CSS Techniques

### 8.1 Modern CSS Features

**Backdrop Blur:**
```jsx
className="backdrop-blur-lg bg-base-100/80"
```

**Aspect Ratio:**
```jsx
className="aspect-square"       // 1:1 aspect ratio
```

**Custom Properties:**
```jsx
className="h-[calc(100vh-8rem)]" // CSS calc() function
className="min-h-[200px]"        // Arbitrary minimum height
className="max-w-[200px]"        // Arbitrary maximum width
```

### 8.2 Spacing System

**Margin and Padding:**
```jsx
className="p-4"                 // 1rem padding all sides
className="px-4"                // 1rem horizontal padding
className="py-3"                // 0.75rem vertical padding
className="pl-10"               // 2.5rem left padding
className="mb-8"                // 2rem bottom margin
className="mt-2"                // 0.5rem top margin
```

**Gap Spacing:**
```jsx
className="gap-2"               // 0.5rem gap
className="gap-2.5"             // 0.625rem gap
className="space-y-4"           // 1rem vertical space between children
className="space-y-6"           // 1.5rem vertical space between children
```

### 8.3 Border and Shadow Effects

**Border Styling:**
```jsx
className="border"              // 1px border
className="border-b"            // Bottom border only
className="border-base-300"     // Theme-based border color
className="rounded-lg"          // Large border radius
className="rounded-xl"          // Extra large border radius
className="rounded-full"        // Full border radius (circle)
className="rounded-2xl"         // 2xl border radius
```

**Shadow Effects:**
```jsx
className="shadow-lg"           // Large shadow
className="shadow-sm"           // Small shadow
className="shadow-cl"           // Custom shadow (typo in original)
```

### 8.4 Layout Utilities

**Overflow Control:**
```jsx
className="overflow-hidden"     // Hide overflow
className="overflow-y-auto"     // Vertical scroll when needed
className="overflow-auto"       // Scroll when needed (both axes)
```

**Z-Index Management:**
```jsx
className="z-40"                // High z-index for fixed elements
```

**Display Properties:**
```jsx
className="hidden"              // Display none
className="flex"                // Display flex
className="grid"                // Display grid
className="block"               // Display block
className="inline"              // Display inline
```

### 8.5 Interactive States

**Disabled States:**
```jsx
className="pointer-events-none" // Disable mouse events
disabled={isLoggingIn}          // HTML disabled attribute
```

**Loading States:**
```jsx
className="animate-pulse pointer-events-none"
```

**Selection States:**
```jsx
className="ring-1 ring-base-300" // Focus/selection ring
```

